Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:36.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}どこかで呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:38.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}近づいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:41.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}真っ白な世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:46.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}たった一つだけの約束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:58.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}きっと忘れないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:02.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}二人過ごした永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:05.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}照れ臭そうに手招く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:09.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}無邪気な時の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}言葉で伝えるには
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:16.79,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}未完成な感情です
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:20.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}運命を嘆くほど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:24.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}私たち弱くはない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:27.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}ねぇそうでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:29.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}どこかで呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:31.68,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}動き出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:34.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}選び取る答えに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:38.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}心ちぎれそうでも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:42.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}守りたいものがあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:46.40,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}ためらいの朝　迷いの夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:49.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}もし手を離しても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:55.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}必ずたどり着くと信じてます
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:24:02.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}私を呼ぶ声が聞こえてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:36.33,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}在某处呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:38.08,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}离我近点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:41.08,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}在纯白的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.08,0:22:46.51,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}只有一个承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:58.44,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我相信你不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:02.31,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我们一起度过的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.31,0:23:05.82,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}你的招呼让我害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:09.90,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}在纯真的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.74,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}要我用言语说明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:16.79,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}是一种不完整的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:20.12,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}命运的叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:24.59,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我们的关系会更脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:27.38,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}嘿，对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:29.80,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}在某处呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:31.68,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}快点来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:34.60,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我不知道怎么回答
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:38.98,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}即使我放下我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:42.73,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}因为有想要守护的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:46.40,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}早上的混乱，晚上的犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:49.44,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}就算放开你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:55.91,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}我相信你会到达那里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:24:02.08,EDTC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\3c&HE6C5A1&}你能听见我的心声吗
